caption: The international students’ welcome is happening in the Chem common room in the Wallberg building (184 College St. - WB238) from 6pm to 8pm on Thursday, September 5th! It will be a great opportunity to meet other international students and learn some tips for success. There will be light refreshments and you get to ask our Chem Club International Inclusivity Directors any burning questions you have! Sign up through the link in our bio!
